#. <section class="sutta" id="an5.107"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an5.107:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 5"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 5"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.107:0.2"
msgid "11. Phāsuvihāravagga"
msgstr "11. Living Comfortably"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: sīlasampannasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an5.107:0.3"
msgid "107. Sīlasutta"
msgstr "107. Ethics"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an5.107:1.1"
msgid "“Pañcahi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu āhuneyyo hoti pāhuneyyo dakkhiṇeyyo añjalikaraṇīyo anuttaraṃ puññakkhettaṃ lokassa."
msgstr "“Mendicants, a mendicant with five factors is worthy of offerings dedicated to the gods, worthy of hospitality, worthy of a religious donation, worthy of veneration with joined palms, and is the supreme field of merit for the world."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an5.107:2.1"
msgid "Katamehi pañcahi?"
msgstr "What five?"

msgctxt "an5.107:2.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sīlasampanno hoti, samādhisampanno hoti, paññāsampanno hoti, vimuttisampanno hoti, vimuttiñāṇadassanasampanno hoti."
msgstr "It’s when a mendicant is accomplished in ethics, immersion, wisdom, freedom, and the knowledge and vision of freedom."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an5.107:3.1"
msgid "Imehi kho, bhikkhave, pañcahi dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu āhuneyyo hoti pāhuneyyo dakkhiṇeyyo añjalikaraṇīyo anuttaraṃ puññakkhettaṃ lokassā”ti."
msgstr "A mendicant with these five qualities is worthy of offerings dedicated to the gods, worthy of hospitality, worthy of a religious donation, worthy of veneration with joined palms, and is the supreme field of merit for the world.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.107:3.2"
msgid "Sattamaṃ."
msgstr ""
